{"type":"message","id":"4d16e444","parentId":"0526191f","timestamp":"2026-03-21T09:10:57.148Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"All done. Let me now provide a concise summary of what was accomplished.","thinkingSignature":"328dca9f80bb3330fd4404eaff32bf81efa3436240c0326f8403468c15700fa4"},{"type":"text","text":"**Subagent 任务完成汇报**\n\n---\n\n### 产出一：day1_3_config.yaml ✅\n\n路径: `quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/config/day1_3_config.yaml`\n\n覆盖内容（与 `rd_agent_integration.yaml` 风格一致）：\n- **信号基本信息**: name/version/description/date_range/author\n- **股票池过滤**: min_price=3.0 / min_total_mv / max_turnover_rate / 涨跌停过滤 / ST排除 / 次新股过滤 / 最低成交额门槛\n- **市场状态门控**: strong (scale=1.0) / neutral (scale=0.6) / weak (scale=0.3)，基于沪深300/MA20趋势判定\n- **仓位规则**: 总仓位72% × regime_scale，单股上限8%，top_k=12\n- **信号输出字段约定**: date / instrument / score / candidates / raw_signal / summary 全部英文字段\n- **接入方式**: overlay 模式，blend权重 day1_3=0.25 / base=0.75\n\n---\n\n### 产出二：Smoke test 通过 ✅\n\n日期: 2026-03-10\n\n| 指标 | 结果 |\n|------|------|\n| 原始股票数 | 5479 |\n| 过过滤器后 | 2192 |\n| 入选候选股 | 12 |\n| 总仓位 | 43.20% |\n| 市场状态 | neutral（trend=-0.0019, scale=0.6） |\n\n产物文件（均已生成到约定目录）：\n- `day1_3_candidates_20260310.csv` — 候选股详情\n- `day1_3_mean_reversion_factor_20260310.csv` — RD因子格式（date/instrument/score）\n- `day1_3_mean_reversion_20260310.csv` — 原始信号（含 risk_flag / strategy_id / generated_at）\n- `day1_3_summary_20260310.json` — 运行摘要\n\n---\n\n### ACTIVE_TASK.md 更新 ✅\n\nNext 第1项（配置文件）和第2项（Smoke test）均已标记为 Completed，并记录了证据文件路径。\n\n**建议下一轮补强方向**：\n1. ret5/dist_ma10/range_pos20 权重 walk-forward 验证\n2. 涨跌停过滤逻辑在脚本中完全落地\n3. 市场宽度（breadth）替代指数趋势作为 regime 判定主指标"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":15378,"output":536,"cacheRead":21089,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37003,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774084244924}}
